Netflix Clone Website

A production-ready streaming platform clone featuring:
- Authentic Netflix-style design and user experience
- Hero section with featured content
- Multiple content carousels (Trending, Popular, My List, etc.)
- Interactive movie cards with detailed hover previews
- Search functionality with live filtering
- Responsive design for all screen sizes
- Smooth animations and micro-interactions
- Netflix color scheme with signature red (#E50914)

Built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS for optimal performance and maintainability.